Each of the huge barrels has been extended out into three rooms - a bedroom, sitting room and bathroom.

The novelty rooms have been decorated with red carpets and curtains - the same colour as the wine they used to house.

They have been completely refurbished to fit in beds, a shower, toilet, mini-bar, TV and - of course - a bottle of red wine on arrival.

